The paper is about local feature detection in computer vision, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses statistical analysis and testing, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of image transformations and the evaluation of detector performance can also be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
